{"response": "Ek chhoti si gaon thi jahan ek chhoti si ladki rehti thi jiska naam Sabala tha. Sabala bahut hi pyaari aur sundar thi, aur usko gaana gane ka bahut shauk tha. Woh har waqt gane gaati thi aur uski aawaz bahut hi khubsurat thi. Lekin, Sabala ek aisi ladki thi jisko log bahut pareshan karte the. Unhone uski aawaz ka mazaak udaya aur usko hasaya. Sabala bahut dukhi ho gayi aur woh gane gaane se darne lagi. 

Ek din, Sabala jungle mein ja rahi thi toh usne ek buddhi aurat ko dekha. Woh aurat bahut hi sundar thi, aur uski aankhon mein ajeeb si chamak thi.  Sabala ne aurat se poochha ki woh kaun hai.  Aurat ne bataaya ki woh ek pari hai, aur woh Sabala ki madad karne aayi hai.  Pari ne Sabala ko bataya ki woh usko gane gaane mein madad karegi, aur usko apni aawaz pe vishwas dilane wali hai. 

Pari ne Sabala ko apna jaadu diya aur Sabala ko bataya ki ab woh gane gaane se kabhi bhi nahin daregi.  Sabala ne pari ka dhanyavaad kiya aur woh apne ghar laut aayi.  Uske baad se, Sabala phir se gane gaane lagi.  Uski aawaz phir se khubsurat ban gayi, aur log uski aawaz sunke bahut hi khush ho gaye.  Sabala ne apne talent pe vishwas karna seekh liya, aur woh phir se khush ho gayi.  Usne samajh liya ki woh kya kar sakti hai aur usne apne talent ka use karna shuru kar diya.  Sabala ki aawaz bahut hi mashoor ho gayi, aur woh ek mashhoor singer ban gayi.  Uski aawaz ne bahut saare logon ko khushi di aur uski aawaz ne unke dil ko chhua.  Sabala bahut khush thi ki usne apne talent pe vishwas karna seekh liya, aur woh apne talent ka use karke bahut saare logon ko khushi de paayi."}

{"response": "Ek baar ek chhote se gaon mein, ek ladka rehta tha jiska naam Tuntun Hero tha.  Woh bahut hi mazboot aur shaktishali tha, lekin woh apni shakti ka galat istemal nahin karta tha.  Woh gaon ke sabhi logon se pyaar karta tha, aur woh hamesha unki madad karta tha.  Ek din, gaon pe ek bada sa aafat aa gaya.  Ek bada sa baaghi jungle se nikal kar gaon pe hamla karne laga.  Baaghi ne gaonwalon ko dhamka kar unke gahane aur paise chura liye.  Gaon ke sabhi log dar gaye aur woh apne gharo mein chhup gaye. 

Tuntun Hero ne yeh dekha aur usne faisla kiya ki woh baaghi se ladkar gaon ko bachayega.  Woh bahut hi himmat se baaghi ke samne khada ho gaya aur usse ladne laga.  Tuntun Hero bahut hi mazboot tha, aur woh baaghi se aasani se lad gaya.  Usne baaghi ko pakad kar police ke hawale kar diya. 

Gaon ke sabhi log bahut khush huye aur unhone Tuntun Hero ka dhanyavaad kiya.  Tuntun Hero ne gaon ko bacha liya aur woh gaon ka hero ban gaya.  Uske baad se, gaon mein koi bhi baaghi nahin aaya, aur sab log khushi se rehne lage. Tuntun Hero hamesha gaon ki raksha karta raha, aur woh gaon ka hero ban kar rehne laga."}

{"response": "Ek bada sa shehar tha, jahan ek brave aur intelligent ladka rehta tha, jiska naam Ajay tha. Ajay hamesha nyay aur sach ke liye ladta tha, aur woh apne sheher ke logo se bahut pyaar karta tha. Ek din, sheher pe ek bada rakshas ne hamla kar diya. Yeh rakshas bahut hi khatarnak tha, aur woh sheher ko barbaad karne pe tulaya hua tha. Sheher ke log dar gaye aur unhone madad ke liye Ajay ko pukara.

Ajay ne apni himmat aur shakti ka use karke rakshas se ladna shuru kar diya. Ladai bahut kathin thi, lekin Ajay himmat nahin haraaya.  Ladai ke beech mein, Ajay ko ek sundar aur himmatwaali ladki mili, jiska naam Simran tha. Simran ek scientist thi, aur usne Ajay ki madad karne ke liye ek special weapon banaya.  Is weapon se, Ajay rakshas ko hara paya. 

Sheher bach gaya, aur Ajay aur Simran dono hero ban gaye. Unki dosti pyaar mein badal gayi, aur unhone shaadi kar li. Unhone ek khushhaal parivaar banaya, aur unki kahani hamesha yaad rakhi gayi."}
